t` + `TranscriptAnalyzer`\\n- **fullAgent** - implements ALL optional interfaces\\n\\nThis pattern prevents exposing methods that the binary doesn't support.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### **2. Protocol Types** (`types.go`)\\n\\n#### **Response Types**\\nEvery subcommand returns JSON-structured responses:\\n\\n| Response Type | Subcommand | Fields |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| `InfoResponse` | info | protocol_version, name, type, description, is_preview, protected_dirs, hook_names, capabilities |\\n| `DetectResponse` | detect | present (bool) |\\n| `SessionIDResponse` | get-session-id | session_id |\\n| `SessionDirResponse` | get-session-dir | session_dir |\\n| `SessionFileResponse` | resolve-session-file | session_file |\\n| `ChunkResponse` | chunk-transcript | chunks ([][]byte) |\\n| `ResumeCommandResponse` | format-resume-command | command |\\n| `HooksInstalledCountResponse` | install-hooks | hooks_installed |\\n| `AreHooksInstalledResponse` | are-hooks-installed | installed |\\n| `TranscriptPositionResponse` | get-transcript-position | position |\\n| `ExtractFilesResponse` | extract-modified-files, extract-all-modified-files | files, current_position |\\n| `ExtractPromptsResponse` | extract-prompts | prompts |\\n| `ExtractSummaryResponse` | extract-summary | summary, has_summary |\\n| `TokenUsageResponse` | calculate-tokens, calculate-total-tokens | input_tokens, cache_creation_tokens, cache_read_tokens, output_tokens, api_call_count, subagent_tokens |\\n| `GenerateTextResponse` | generate-text | text |\\n\\n#### **Complex JSON Types**\\n\\n**AgentSessionJSON** - Transfer format for agent.AgentSession:\\n```go\\ntype AgentSessionJSON struct {\\n    SessionID     string   `json:\\\"session_id\\\"`\\n    AgentName     string   `json:\\\"agent_name\\\"`\\n    RepoPath      string   `json:\\\"repo_path\\\"`\\n    SessionRef    string   `json:\\\"session_ref\\\"`\\n    StartTime     string   `json:\\\"start_time\\\"` // RFC3339 format\\n    NativeData    []byte   `json:\\\"native_data\\\"`\\n    ModifiedFiles []string `json:\\\"modified_files\\\"`\\n    NewFiles      []string `json:\\\"new_files\\\"`\\n    DeletedFiles  []string `json:\\\"deleted_files\\\"`\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**eventJSON** - Transfer format for agent.Event:\\n```go\\ntype eventJSON struct {\\n    Type              int               `json:\\\"type\\\"`\\n    SessionID         string            `json:\\\"session_id\\\"`\\n    PreviousSessionID string            `json:\\\"previous_session_id,omitempty\\\"`\\n    SessionRef        string            `json:\\\"session_ref,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Prompt            string            `json:\\\"prompt,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Model             string            `json:\\\"model,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Timestamp         string            `json:\\\"timestamp,omitempty\\\"` // RFC3339\\n    ToolUseID         string            `json:\\\"tool_use_id,omitempty\\\"`\\n    SubagentID        string            `json:\\\"subagent_id,omitempty\\\"`\\n    ToolInput         json.RawMessage   `json:\\\"tool_input,omitempty\\\"`\\n    SubagentType      string            `json:\\\"subagent_type,omitempty\\\"`\\n    TaskDescription   string            `json:\\\"task_description,omitempty\\\"`\\n    ResponseMessage   string            `json:\\\"response_message,omitempty\\\"`\\n    Metadata          map[string]string `json:\\\"metadata,omitempty\\\"`\\n}\\n\\n// Conversion method:\\nfunc (ej *eventJSON) toEvent() (*agent.Event, error)\\n```\\n\\n**HookInputJSON** - Transfer format for agent.HookInput:\\n```go\\ntype HookInputJSON struct {\\n    HookType   string                 `json:\\\"hook_type\\\"`\\n    SessionID  string                 `json:\\\"session_id\\\"`\\n    SessionRef string                 `json:\\\"session_ref\\\"`\\n    Timestamp  string                 `json:\\\"timestamp\\\"` // RFC3339\\n    UserPrompt string                 `json:\\\"user_prompt,omitempty\\\"`\\n    ToolName   string                 `json:\\\"tool_name,omitempty\\\"`\\n    ToolUseID  s