alAgentSession(j *AgentSessionJSON) (*agent.AgentSession, error)\\nfunc convertTokenUsage(r *TokenUsageResponse) *agent.TokenUsage\\n```\\n\\n#### **Time Handling**\\n- All timestamps serialized as RFC3339 format (`time.RFC3339`)\\n- Parsed back with `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, string)`\\n\\n#### **Environment Setup**\\nEvery subcommand execution sets:\\n- `ENTIRE_PROTOCOL_VERSION=1`\\n- `ENTIRE_REPO_ROOT=<repo-root-path>`\\n- Working directory = repo root\\n\\n#### **Error Handling**\\n- Exit code 0 = success\\n- Non-zero exit = error\\n- stderr captured and wrapped in error message\\n- Subcommand name prefixed to errors (e.g., \\\"chunk-transcript: ...\\\")\\n\\n#### **Null Event Handling**\\n`ParseHookEvent` returns `nil, nil` when hook output is `null` (no lifecycle significance)\\n\\n---\\n\\n### **13. Type Constants** (`agent/registry.go`)\\n\\n```go\\nconst (\\n    AgentNameClaudeCode     types.AgentName = \\\"claude-code\\\"\\n    AgentNameCursor         types.AgentName = \\\"cursor\\\"\\n    AgentNameGemini         types.AgentName = \\\"gemini\\\"\\n    AgentNameOpenCode       types.AgentName = \\\"opencode\\\"\\n    AgentNameFactoryAIDroid types.AgentName = \\\"factoryai-droid\\\"\\n)\\n\\nconst (\\n    AgentTypeClaudeCode     types.AgentType = \\\"Claude Code\\\"\\n    AgentTypeCursor         types.AgentType = \\\"Cursor\\\"\\n    AgentTypeGemini         types.AgentType = \\\"Gemini CLI\\\"\\n    AgentTypeOpenCode       types.AgentType = \\\"OpenCode\\\"\\n    AgentTypeFactoryAIDroid types.AgentType = \\\"Factory AI Droid\\\"\\n    AgentTypeUnknown        types.AgentType = \\\"Agent\\\"\\n)\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\nThis comprehensive analysis covers:\\n- External agent discovery and registration mechanism\\n- Complete protocol subcommand specification\\n- All JSON types for request/response serialization\\n- Agent interface hierarchy (core + optional interfaces)\\n- Transcript parsing and chunking utilities\\n- Time/JSON formatting conventions\\n- Type constants